(379, '2016-02-23 20:25:40', '2016-03-23 09:33:56', 'NEXIUM 20mg ', 'nexium-20mg', '103805 ', '                     <ul>      <li><em><span style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">Bệnh tr&agrave;o ngược dạ d&agrave;y - thực quản (GERD)</span><br style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" />      </em></li>      <li><em><span style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/15px Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px">Bệnh nh&acirc;n cần điều trị bằng NSAID li&ecirc;n tục</span></em></li>  </ul>                ', '             	<p><strong>Chỉ định:</strong></p>  <p><span style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">Bệnh tr&agrave;o ngược dạ d&agrave;y - thực quản (GERD)</span><br style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" />  &nbsp; <span style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">- Điều trị vi&ecirc;m sướt thực quản do tr&agrave;o ngược.<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><br style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" />  &nbsp; <span style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">- Điều trị d&agrave;i hạn do bệnh nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;m thực quản đ&atilde; chữa l&agrave;nh để ph&ograve;ng ngừa t&aacute;i ph&aacute;t.</span><br style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" />  &nbsp; <span style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">- Điều trị chứng bệnh tr&agrave;o ngược dạ d&agrave;y - thực quản (GERD)</span><br style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" />  <span style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">Kết hợp với một ph&aacute;c đồ kh&aacute;ng khuẩn th&iacute;ch hợp để diệt trừ Helicobacter pylori l&agrave; nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n g&acirc;y nhiễm tr&ugrave;ng v&agrave; vi&ecirc;m lo&eacute;t</span>.<br style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" />  <span style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">Bệnh nh&acirc;n cần điều trị bằng NSAID li&ecirc;n tục:<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><br style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" />  &nbsp; <span style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">- Chữa l&agrave;nh lo&eacute;t dạ d&agrave;y do d&ugrave;ng thuốc NSAID</span><br style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px" />  &nbsp; <span style="widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; display: inline !important; font: 12px/15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px">- Ph&ograve;ng ngừa lo&eacute;t dạ d&agrave;y v&agrave; lo&eacute;t t&aacute; tr&agrave;ng do d&ugrave;ng thuốc NSAID ở bệnh nh&acirc;n c&oacute; nguy cơ.</span></p>  <p>&nbsp;</p>            ', '259000', 'public/crawler/nexium-20mgd35127fd9b2196d7f2fd5e5ee371462a.png', '', 'Hộp 14 viên ', 11),
